PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION (a) to sell some real property to the Regional Municipality of OTTAWA-CARLETON consisting of a strip of land situated along Sawmill Creek in the City of Ottawa, Ontario, for the purposes of the SOUTH-EAST TRANSITWAY, and (b) to grant two easements to the Municipality for the installation of a water main and other storm drainage works required in connection therewith.
